# ZeroBETH – License Information

ZeroBETH is an open-source badminton stringing machine firmware and hardware system, developed and maintained by **KuoKuo**.

- Hardware License: [CERN-OHL-W v2](https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_w_v2.txt)  
- Software License: [GNU General Public License v3.0](https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt)

Project Homepage: https://github.com/206cc/ZeroBETH  
Contact: 500119.cpc@gmail.com

